\c 23
\s Amazwi okucina kaDavida
\p
\v 1 La-ke ngamazwi okucina kaDavida. UDavida indodana kaJese wathi\x + Nani 24.3,15.\x*, lomuntu ophakanyiselwe phezulu\x + 7.8,9. Hlab. 78.70,71.\x*, ogcotshiweyo kaNkulunkulu kaJakobe\x + 1 Sam. 16.12,13. Hlab. 89.20.\x*, lomhlabeleli omnandi wakoIsrayeli, wathi:
\v 2 UMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* wakhuluma ngami, lelizwi lakhe lisolimini lwami\x + 2 Pet. 1.21.\x*.
\v 3 UNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli wathi, iDwala likaIsrayeli lakhuluma kimi \add lathi\x + 22.3,32. Dute. 32.4.\x*\add*: Obusa abantu \add uzakuba\add* ngolungileyo, ebusa \add ngo\add*kumesaba uNkulunkulu\x + Eks. 18.21. 2 Lan. 19.9.\x*.
\v 4 Njalo \add uzakuba\add* njengokukhanya kwekuseni \add e\add*kuphum\add eni\add* kwelanga\x + Hlu. 5.31. Zaga 4.18. Hlab. 110.3.\x*, ikuseni engelamayezi, \add njeng\add*ohlaza emhlabathini ngokukhanya emva kwezulu.
\v 5 Lanxa indlu yami ingenjalo kuNkulunkulu, kube kanti wenzile lami isivumelwano esilaphakade, esimiswe kuhle ezintweni zonke, lesigcinekileyo\x + 7.15,16. Hlab. 89.29. Isa. 55.3.\x*, ngoba lonke usindiso lwami lesiloyiso \add sikuso\add*, lanxa engasikhulisi\x + Gen. 3.18.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Kodwa \add aba\add*kaBheliyali bonke banjengameva alahliweyo\x + Jobe 34.18. Nah. 1.15. Dute. 13.13. 15.9.\x*, ngoba engelakuthathwa ngesandla;
\v 7 kodwa umuntu owathintayo uzazihlomisa ngensimbi langoluthi lomkhonto\x + 21.19.\x*, azatshiswa lokutshiswa ngomlilo kuleyondawo.
\s Amaqhawe kaDavida
\p
\v 8 La ngamabizo amaqhawe uDavida ayelawo\x + 1 Lan. 11.10-41.\x*: UJoshebi-Bashebeti umTahekemoni, inhloko yezinduna; nguye uAdino umEzini, ngenxa yabangamakhulu ayisificaminwembili ababulawa ngasikhathi sinye\x + Eks. 14.7. 15.4.\x*.
\v 9 Lemva kwakhe kwakuloEleyazare indodana kaDodo indodana kaAhohi, owamaqhawe amathathu \add aye\add*loDavida\x + 1 Lan. 11.12-14. 27.4.\x*, ekudeleleni kwabo amaFilisti ayebuthanele khona impi, lapho amadoda akoIsrayeli esenyukile\x + 21.21.\x*,
\v 10 yena wasukuma watshaya amaFilisti saze sadinwa isandla sakhe, lesandla sakhe sanamathela enkembeni. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisenza usindiso olukhulu ngalolosuku; abantu basebebuya emva kwakhe ukuzaphanga kuphela\x + 23.12. 19.2.\x*.
\v 11 Lemva kwakhe kwakuloShama indodana kaAge umHarari\x + 1 Lan. 11.27. 1 Lan. 11.13,14.\x*. AmaFilisti ayebuthene aba lixuku, lapho okwakukhona isiqinti sensimu sigcwele amalentili; njalo abantu babaleka ebusweni bamaFilisti,
\v 12 kodwa wajama phakathi kwesiqinti, wasivikela, wawatshaya amaFilisti. IN\nd kosi\nd* yenza-ke usindiso olukhulu\x + 23.12. 19.2.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Abathathu ezinhlokweni ezingamatshumi amathathu basebesehla, bafika kuDavida ebhalwini lweAdulamu\x + 1 Sam. 22.1.\x* ngesikhathi sokuvuna; lexuku lamaFilisti lalimise inkamba esihotsheni seRefayimi\x + 5.18.\x*.
\v 14 Langalesosikhathi uDavida wayesenqabeni\x + 5.7,17. 1 Sam. 22.4,5.\x*, lebutho lenqaba lamaFilisti lali\add se\add*Bhethelehema ngalesosikhathi\x + 1 Sam. 13.23.\x*.
\v 15 UDavida wasenxwanela, wathi: Hawu, kungathi omunye ubenganginathisa amanzi omthombo weBhethelehema ongasesangweni!
\v 16 Lawomaqhawe amathathu asefohla adabula enkambeni yamaFilisti, akha amanzi emthonjeni weBhethelehema owawungasesangweni, awathatha awaletha kuDavida. Kube kanti kathandanga ukuwanatha, kodwa wawathululela iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 17 Wasesithi: Kakube khatshana lami, N\nd kosi\nd*, ukuthi ngenze lokho; \add kakusi\add*gazi yini labantu abahambe lempilo yabo \add engozini\add*? Ngalokho kathandanga ukuwanatha. Lezizinto azenza lamaqhawe amathathu\x + Levi 17.10.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Njalo uAbishayi, umfowabo kaJowabi indodana kaZeruya, wayeyinhloko yabathathu. Yena wasegiyela abangamakhulu amathathu ngomkhonto wakhe, ababuleweyo, wasesiba lebizo phakathi kwabathathu.
\v 19 Kahlonitshwanga kakhulu yini kulabathathu? Ngakho waba yinduna yabo; kodwa kafikanga kwabathathu \add abokuqala\x + 23.23. 1 Lan. 11.21.\x*\add*.
\v 20 UBhenaya-ke, indodana kaJehoyada, indodana yeqhawe\x + 23.22. 8.18. 20.23.\x*, omkhulu ngezenzo, weKabhiseyeli\x + Josh. 15.21.\x*. Yena watshaya ababili abanjengezilwane bakoMowabi\x + Eks. 15.15.\x*; futhi wehla watshaya isilwane phakathi komgodi mhla weliqhwa elikhithikileyo.
\v 21 Yena wasetshaya indoda engumGibhithe, umuntu obukekayo; njalo umGibhithe wayelomkhonto esandleni sakhe; kodwa wehlela kuye elenduku, wawuhluthuna umkhonto esandleni somGibhithe, wambulala ngomkhonto wakhe.
\v 22 Lezizinto wazenza uBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada, waba lebizo phakathi kwamaqhawe amathathu.
\v 23 Wayehlonipheka kulabangamatshumi amathathu, kodwa kafikanga kwabathathu\x + 23.19.\x*. UDavida wasembeka phezu kwabalindi bakhe.
\p
\v 24 UAsaheli umfowabo kaJowabi wayephakathi kwabangamatshumi amathathu\x + 2.18. 1 Lan. 27.7.\x*, uElihanani indodana kaDodo weBhethelehema,
\v 25 uShama umHarodi, uElika umHarodi\x + Hlu. 7.1. 1 Lan. 11.27. 27.8.\x*,
\v 26 uHelezi umPaliti\x + Josh. 15.27.\x*, uIra indodana kaIkheshi umThekhowa\x + 14.2.\x*,
\v 27 uAbiyezeri umAnethothi\x + Josh. 21.18.\x*, uMebunayi umHusha\x + 21.18.\x*,
\v 28 uZalimoni umAhohi\x + 23.9. 1 Lan. 11.12,29. 27.4. 1 Lan. 8.4.\x*, uMaharayi umNetofa\x + 2 Kho. 25.23.\x*,
\v 29 uHelebi indodana kaBahana umNetofa\x + 2 Kho. 25.23.\x*, uIthayi indodana kaRibayi weGibeya wabantwana bakoBhenjamini\x + Hlu. 19.13,14. Josh. 18.28.\x*,
\v 30 uBhenaya umPirathoni\x + Hlu. 12.13,15. 1 Lan. 27.14.\x*, uHidayi wezifuleni zeGahashi\x + Josh. 24.30. Hlu. 2.9.\x*,
\v 31 uAbi-Aliboni umAraba\x + Josh. 18.18.\x*, uAzimavethi umBahurimi\x + 3.16.\x*,
\v 32 uEliyabha umShahaliboni\x + Josh. 19.42. 1 Kho. 4.9.\x*, wamadodana kaJasheni, uJonathani,
\v 33 uShama umHarari, uAhiyamu indodana kaSharari umHarari\x + 23.11.\x*,
\v 34 uElifeleti indodana kaAhasibayi indodana yomMahaka\x + 10.6,8.\x*, uEliyamu indodana kaAhithofeli umGilo\x + 11.3. 15.12.\x*,
\v 35 uHezirayi umKharmeli\x + Josh. 15.55.\x*, uPaharayi umArabi,
\v 36 uIgali indodana kaNathani weZoba\x + 8.3.\x*, uBani umGadi,
\v 37 uZeleki umAmoni\x + 10.1. 17.27.\x*, uNaharayi umBherothi\x + 4.2.\x*, umthwali wezikhali zikaJowabi indodana kaZeruya,
\v 38 uIra\x + 20.26.\x* umIthiri\x + Josh. 15.48. 1 Lan. 2.53.\x*, uGarebi umIthiri,
\v 39 uUriya umHethi\x + 11.6.\x*; \add be\add*bonke \add babe\add*ngamatshumi amathathu lesikhombisa.